{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876020/extras/LibraryGif.gif?t=1739393922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Psychological horror and suffocating inmersive gameplay is what your are  gonna find in <strong>The Rite</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Narrative</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Would you defy death for the one you love?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Alex lost his wife under mysterious circumstances\u2014memories blurred by a life of excess and grief. Desperate to bring her back, he performed a forbidden rite\u2026 but it went horribly wrong. Now, her vengeful spirit haunts their home, twisting his memories and leaving him trapped in a nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unravel the truth behind her death, navigate a house consumed by darkness, and survive the horrors that lurk within.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Uncover the dark truth behind Alex's wife's death in this horror experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a haunted house filled with sinister secrets, solve intricate puzzles, and switch between worlds to survive. But beware\u2014the vengeful spirit is always watching. Find the objects needed to perform the rite, outsmart the horrors that lurk in the shadows, and escape this corrupted nightmare\u2026 if you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876020/extras/Find.gif?t=1739393922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feel free to explore and search for objects in the house to unlock interactions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets